{
    "info": {
        "name": "2. WorkFitAI - Application Service",
        "_postman_id": "application-service-collection",
        "description": "# Application Service API\n\nJob application management endpoints for WorkFitAI Platform.\n\n## Architecture\nThis service uses **event-driven architecture** with Kafka. All state changes publish events for downstream services.\n\n## Authentication\nAll endpoints require JWT authentication. The username is extracted from the JWT `sub` claim.\n\n## Roles & Permissions\n| Role | Permissions |\n|------|-------------|\n| CANDIDATE | Create, view own, withdraw applications |\n| HR | View job applications, update status |\n| ADMIN | Full access |\n\n## Status Flow\n```\nAPPLIED → REVIEWING → INTERVIEW → OFFER → HIRED\n                ↘ REJECTED (at any stage)\n```\n\n## Kafka Events\n| Event | Topic | Trigger |\n|-------|-------|--------|\n| APPLICATION_CREATED | application-events | New application |\n| STATUS_CHANGED | application-status | Status update |\n| APPLICATION_WITHDRAWN | application-events | Withdrawal |",
        "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
    },
    "variable": [
        {
            "key": "baseUrl",
            "value": "http://localhost:9085",
            "description": "API Gateway URL"
        },
        {
            "key": "service_base",
            "value": "{{baseUrl}}/application",
            "description": "Application service base URL"
        }
    ],
